nodes.text: 2016 Topps Star Wars: The Force Awakens Series 2

Star Wars The Force Awakens Series 2 was a trading card set released by The Topps Company, Inc. in 2016 to coincide with the release of the Star Wars saga film Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens. The set featured 102 base cards, autograph cards, and a limited set of concept art cards.
